param.name: override
param.description: An optional URL to override the class's annotated endpoint information.

param.name: params
param.description: An optional set of parameters to be interpolated into the URL, when placeholders are used.

param.name: query
param.description: An optional set of query parameters to append to the end of the EndpointObject URL.

return.description: Returns a Collection of EndpointObject objects; empty if none are found.
